1.title: Pagsisimula
1.plot: After celebrating her 59th birthday, Gloria Guerrero-Alegre travels back to Cervantes and starts recalling her bittersweet memories with her first love, Peter Alcantara.

2.title: Hindi nabunyag
2.plot: On her trip back to Cervantes, Gloria visits Peter's favorite place and remembers the promises they made with each other. Meanwhile, Gloria's grandson, Z, comes up with an idea for her next birthday.

3.title: Sorpresa
3.plot: The Alegre siblings make up for their absence on Gloria's birthday by setting up a surprise party the day after.
